<h1 class="display-4 text-center mt-5">Del Monte Motor Works, Inc.</h1>
<p class="h6 fw-normal text-center mt-2">
    Del Monte Motor Works, Inc. (DMMW), also known as Del Monte Motors, is a bus and truck manufacturer headquartered in Quezon City, Philippines.
    It was established in 1950. The company offers a range of truck and bus bodies for its all major brands.
    It is also one of the leading bus body manufacturers in the Philippines. Galleries below are some of its notable bus models.
</p>

